            <title>[CASSANDRA-9731] PartitionTest.testColumnStatsRecordsRowDeletesCorrectly is flappy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9731</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/trunk_utest/350/testReport/junit/org.apache.cassandra.db/PartitionTest/testColumnStatsRecordsRowDeletesCorrectly/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;This run of trunk-testall&lt;/a&gt; failed for &lt;tt&gt;PartitionTest.testColumnStatsRecordsRowDeletesCorrectly&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

