                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14636965" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 22 Jul 2015 14:14:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, that patch probably work most of the time, but it&apos;s a bit of a hack. Besides, what we want is test that the stats capture what we&apos;ve inserted, not &quot;something close enough&quot;, so I think the right fix is to pass the localDeletionTime we want to the &lt;tt&gt;deleteRow&lt;/tt&gt; call. Attaching v2 that does that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14637295" author="snazy" created="Wed, 22 Jul 2015 17:56:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Your patch LGTM - yea, it&apos;s the better solution.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14638339" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 23 Jul 2015 07:01:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Alright, committed then, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
